text:
"Papa ji ko kaise jaante ho" that is all it took to find a life long friend
Tere 95% decisions ekdum sahi hote hai the other 5 contain stocks lena, Antaragni mein pussy ban jana pure time, sochna ki tu time par uth jayega kabhi bahar jaane ke liye , 1st year ka woh infamous haircut and not so many more. Kuch bhi krle sports mein toh mein hi better rahunga terese :P
Tu bus Covid khatam hone de seedha Patiala aakar harunga tujhe, Jo dosti lockdown mein thandi na hui woh humesha ke liye <3
author: Bhavy  Singh

text:
"Bhut kum log hote hai jo dost ko emotionally bhi sambhal le aur ladai ke time physically bhi" yeh tere upar ekdum perfect baithta hai bhai.
Tere gentleman and charming nature ka toh mein bhut bada fan hu dost, and yes uss raat kya baraf ke maze liye the bean bag se xD. Ek din phirse arm wrestle knockouts satta bhi karenge and lastly apni bet is ON ! bhut hype up kar diya hai isse ab jaldi trip banao.
author: Bhavy  Singh
